# UI Design Standard
- Color: Primary #2563eb (Blue), Background #f8fafc (Slate-50).
- Component Style: Rounded corners (xl), subtle borders (slate-200), card-based containers.
- Typography: Use Inter or sans-serif. Labels should be small and muted.
- Layout: Max width 1200px, consistent padding (p-6), use Grid for forms (2-3 columns).
- Interactive: Buttons should have subtle scale-down effect on click.
